{
  "stem": "2435.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It did help in a way, but I think the main thing that helped was that letter from the old doctor who had written a letter of good health that was accompanying the-- you see, there was a letter of good health and of good-- and of good-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that one was not a robber or anything, you know?",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Character.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Character, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I finally got the visa, that was in February, '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "February, '41, which was really the last minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had already, before that, packed quite a few things which we were allowed to take.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many of the things we were not allowed to take and leave-- left it with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not allowed-- for instance, we were not allowed to take any jewelry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have much jewelry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No cutlery-- silver cutlery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was all staying in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, yeah, glasses and things we were allowed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were not allowed-- the furniture, of course, was staying behind, which we didn't care.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, we were so eager to get out now, finally, that we didn't care what we left in Germany, except my poor grandma.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when we came to America, of course, we tried urgently to get my grandmother over, to get a visa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We never were able to get her one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April-- April 15, 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went via [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Germany for, I think, 36 hours through Germany and through France-- occupied France, occupied with the-- the trains were all darkened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Spain and Portugal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went from Portugal, Lisbon, on the which was a big ship which took us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were-- the-- the trains were darkened because of the-- we were not allowed to see any military significance in-- in France, you see.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
